'''''Star Wars Weekly'' 117''' is the one hundred seventeenth issue of the [[Marvel Comics|Marvel UK]]'s ''[[Star Wars Weekly]]'' series of comic reprints. Starting with the next issue, the series would be renamed ''[[The Empire Strikes Back Weekly]]'', but would continue the numbering used under the previous title. This was first time detailed in [[Star Wars Weekly 116|''Star Wars Weekly'' 116]] by a [[C-3PO]] and [[R2-D2]] advert.

==Contents==
*[[Star Wars (1977) 38|''Star Wars'' (1977) 38]] {{C|Part 2}}
*Heroes of the galaxy: Man-Wolf Part 4: Man-Wolf shows his claws!
*Deathlok the Demolisher Part 27: The final chapter!
*Tales of the Watcher: The treasure of Planetoid 12!

